statement.p:
Let e^0,e^1,e^2,\ldots be the sequences from . Show that
a\in\mathrm{span}\{e^0,e^1,e^2,\ldots\}
if and only if a is finitely supported.

Consider polynomials \{a_ix^3+b_ix^2+c_ix+d_i : i=1,2,3,4.\} Show that this collection of polynomials is linearly independent if and only if
\begin{bmatrix} a_1 \amp b_1 \amp c_1 \amp d_1 \\ a_2 \amp b_2 \amp c_2 \amp d_2 \\ a_3 \amp b_3 \amp c_3 \amp d_3 \\ a_4 \amp b_4 \amp c_4 \amp d_4 \end{bmatrix}
is an invertible matrix.
